flowchart LR
    A1[Service A: submit intent]
    A2[Service A: receive intent_id]
    A3[Service A: read events]
    A4[Service A: terminal outcome]

    X1[AXME Cloud: CREATED → SUBMITTED → DELIVERED]
    X2[AXME Cloud: ACKNOWLEDGED → IN_PROGRESS]
    X3{AXME Cloud: blocked?}
    X4[AXME Cloud: WAITING\nhuman / tool / agent / time]
    X5[AXME Cloud: resume or scheduler tick]
    X6[AXME Cloud: COMPLETED / FAILED / CANCELED]

    B1[Service B: intent received]
    B2[Service B: async execution]
    B3[Service B: status / completion event]

    A1 --> X1
    X1 --> A2 & B1
    B1 --> B2 --> B3
    A3 & B3 --> X2
    X2 --> X3
    X3 -->|yes| X4 --> X5 --> X2
    X3 -->|no|  X6
    X6 --> A4
